{"tid":788204,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我個ex攞我d錢去嫖妓","createTime":"2018-08-21T09:38:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T14:47:26.000Z","uid":183265,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7659804829b62dfaee6e9bffc874302808778542","tid":788204,"uid":183265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T09:38:04.000Z","msg":"係咁既 同男朋友拍左三年拖 最後不歡而散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  分左手之後 [size=3] 佢走黎問我借錢 話佢需要一筆錢去應急<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  起初我都唔借 念住唔想再同佢扯上關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過見佢d語氣好似好凝重 最後都借左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  後來重點黎啦 佢d朋友同我講佢攞左我筆錢去叫雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  之後我緊係問佢攞翻d錢啦 佢不斷扯開話題 仲同我講佢同隻臭雞咩都冇做過 仲問我可唔可以俾個機會佢復合 佢係咪痴撚左線 唔係似為我會信呀？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢老母西 仲要完全毫無悔意 講嘢超級輕佻 係咁話 咁最後都冇做過野啦  尋開心有咩問題 佢覺得佢咁樣做係冇問題 想搵人返箍煲一d誠意都冇 仲覺得自己比雞呃好慘咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec77f6f573961e20a59dcb4902c5ffc449ca9528","tid":788204,"uid":198583,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T09:50:00.000Z","msg":"你都係臭雞"},{"pid":"0cd56a790af83729a16ebfa2bcd85cfd9b7110af","tid":788204,"uid":59848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T09:51:05.000Z","msg":"咁嘅人你最初點睇得上眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6accb5723f7165603ff254b2efa091f3c8d511f",